Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.31,0:00:04.75,Matsumoto,Matsumoto,0,0,0,,As the boke I'm worried for my job
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.43,0:00:09.42,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Hamada Masatoshi Senility Trial
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.18,0:00:14.23,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,This king of comedy will turn 51 this year,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.08,0:00:18.16,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,But his senility will not stop
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:20.84,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,His "old man-ness" will be exposed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.84,0:00:23.24,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Incident #1
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.50,0:00:30.40,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,It was an episode where they enjoyed nostalgic games
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.51,0:00:32.91,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,They have bang snaps too!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.36,0:00:38.75,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Hamada found some bang snaps, that make a loud bang when you throw them
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.56,0:00:43.74,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,He hatched a plan to scare Endo,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.74,0:00:46.73,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,He approached with the Bang Snaps
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.51,0:00:49.09,Yamasaki,Yamasaki,0,0,0,,There's ice cream-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.50,0:00:59.32,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,He tried to throw them to the ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.32,0:01:02.91,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,But he misjudged the distance to the table
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.91,0:01:05.01,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Indeed, an onset of senility
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.01,0:01:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Incident #2
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.18,0:01:12.78,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Broadcasted in April, TKO Kinoshita's Shichi Henge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.55,0:01:16.07,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Pay attention to Hamada's front teeth,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.69,0:01:17.89,Matsumoto,Matsumoto,0,0,0,,This was there the whole time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.09,0:01:21.73,Endo,Endo,0,0,0,,Right in the middle?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.25,0:01:24.90,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,He did not notice,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.90,0:01:29.49,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,There was some spring onion stuck between his front teeth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.49,0:01:30.80,Yamasaki,Unknown,0,0,0,,In the centre?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.80,0:01:32.80,Matsumoto,Matsumoto,0,0,0,,Spring onion is stuck in there,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.13,0:01:35.61,Matsumoto,Matsumoto,0,0,0,,And he didn't notice it,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.61,0:01:37.88,Matsumoto,Matsumoto,0,0,0,,It's GREEN!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.88,0:01:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Incident #3
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.00,0:01:44.14,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,A birthday gift to his junior,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.00,0:01:52.56,Black Text,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\pos(733.43,260.497)}The tangerine says "Otanbi Omedetou" instead of "OtanJOUbi Omedetou" (Happy Birthday)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.64,0:01:48.52,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,I didn't notice at all
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.85,0:01:52.56,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,His senility caused him to forget the most important character
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.56,0:01:58.90,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,Don't you feel relieved after writing the "TAN"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:01.13,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,I mean that kanji-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.13,0:02:02.83,Matsumoto,Matsumoto,0,0,0,,That's a great proverb
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.83,0:02:06.44,Matsumoto,Matsumoto,0,0,0,,"One feels relieved after writing OTAN"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.44,0:02:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Incident #4
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.85,0:02:16.97,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Hamada misunderstood the size and came in wearing a ladies T-shirt
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.52,0:02:22.09,Black Text,,0,0,0,,{\pos(976.663,745.801)}Victim - Kimura Yuichi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.31,0:02:22.09,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,The victim explains what happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.38,0:02:24.29,Kimura,Kimura,0,0,0,,In the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.26,0:02:28.53,Kimura,Kimura,0,0,0,,It was like a ballet dancer's practice outfit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.23,0:02:32.03,Kimura,Kimura,0,0,0,,The shirt barely reached his belly button
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.03,0:02:35.13,Kimura,Kimura,0,0,0,,It short and tight,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.27,0:02:39.10,Kimura,Kimura,0,0,0,,I was quite sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.44,0:02:42.17,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,If that was a ladies,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.17,0:02:46.34,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,It was just right
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.34,0:02:50.65,Matsumoto,Matsumoto,0,0,0,,Another great proverb
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:57.66,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,And tonight, more senility incidents will be exposed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.66,0:03:02.26,Endo,Endo,0,0,0,,We have a junior comedian here who looks up to Hamada,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:04.37,Endo,Endo,0,0,0,,We've collected testimonies,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.37,0:03:06.42,Endo,Endo,0,0,0,,and a representative is here,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.59,0:03:07.58,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.42,0:03:07.95,Endo,Endo,0,0,0,,Is that alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.57,0:03:08.83,Judge Nakamura,Judge Nakamura,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.65,0:03:10.96,Judge Nakamura,Judge Nakamura,0,0,0,,Witness, enter please
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.73,0:03:11.37,Black Text,,0,0,0,,Presiding Judge\NNAKAMURA Yoshinobu   Producer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:14.11,Tomonori,,0,0,0,,Hello,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.87,0:03:16.11,Default,Tomonori,0,0,0,,Witness\NJinnai Tomonori
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:15.55,Default,Crowd,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:16.88,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,What the hell man
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.44,0:03:18.56,Matsumoto,Matsumoto,0,0,0,,JInnai will be the representative,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.56,0:03:22.10,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,That's correct\N In order to present evidence against the defendant,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.10,0:03:27.85,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,I have collected testimonies from various junior comedians
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:29.85,Matsumoto,Matsumoto,0,0,0,,To provide a judgement,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.75,0:03:29.89,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,Yes indeed,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.12,0:03:33.56,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Testimonies from junior comedians,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:38.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Jinnai will reveal some shocking senile moments!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:42.60,Tomonori Text,Tomonori,0,0,0,,In honesty, there are many young comedians who admire Hamada,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.60,0:03:47.61,Tomonori Text,Tomonori,0,0,0,,In fact, I WAS one of them,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.00,0:03:45.97,Yamasaki,Yamasaki,0,0,0,,WAS?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:47.38,Endo,Endo,0,0,0,,You say that in past tense?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.61,0:03:52.01,Tomonori Text,Tomonori,0,0,0,,I was dissapointed in a lot of his actions,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.22,0:03:50.56,Matsumoto,Matsumoto,0,0,0,,There's a lot there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.74,0:03:52.01,Endo,Endo,0,0,0,,So you've lost respect?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.05,0:03:56.77,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,First off, "Incident #1 - A Meal Time Disaster"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.77,0:04:01.59,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,Hamada has treated many of his juniors to dinner,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.78,0:04:05.26,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,But there are many senile moments that occured at those meals
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:07.46,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,Ready? This is it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.63,0:04:12.89,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,"Knocking over a transparent glass with water inside it"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.16,0:04:11.60,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(703.585,433.536)}Knocking over a transparent glass with water inside it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.80,0:04:18.80,Matsumoto,Matsumoto,0,0,0,,Transparent things are invisible to him
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.83,0:04:17.97,Tomonori,,0,0,0,,He can't see them
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.67,0:04:18.80,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Just invisible
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:21.21,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,Transparent things are invisble,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.87,0:04:21.96,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.94,0:04:27.01,Tomonori Text,,0,0,0,,he went " WHAT WAS THAT?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.21,0:04:27.01,Tomonori Text,,0,0,0,,When he knocked it over,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.01,0:04:29.35,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,He was surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.05,0:04:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.74,0:04:32.18,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,So, moving on,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.18,0:04:35.18,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,"Satisfied after 3 pieces of meat"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.74,0:04:37.18,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,This story,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.18,0:04:39.76,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,Hamada and his juniors,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.76,0:04:44.81,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,They had dinner at a Teppenyaki place, \N Being considerate of Hamada,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.81,0:04:48.10,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,"Should we reduce the size of our order?" they asked him
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:49.56,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,and Hamada said,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.08,0:04:52.87,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,"Don't treat me like an old man! The standard is fine!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.87,0:04:54.71,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,He was a bit angry
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.71,0:04:56.44,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,So they ate the meat,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.44,0:04:59.51,Tomonori Text,Tomonori,0,0,0,,But after 3 pieces of meat; "Damn I'm so full"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.51,0:05:05.15,Tomonori Text,Tomonori,0,0,0,,and then he dozed off
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:05.23,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,I've been told this happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.23,0:05:06.84,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,What do you mean "Dozed off"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.84,0:05:09.32,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,That's what an actual old man would do
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.32,0:05:10.85,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,This is what I've been told
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:12.63,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,It's a shock indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.80,0:05:14.83,Matsumoto,Matsumoto,0,0,0,,I wish we saw his meat loving side more there
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:20.34,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,There's other dishes, before the meat. There's other courses,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.34,0:05:21.47,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,So it's not like,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.10,0:05:23.60,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,Dozing off, and such
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.60,0:05:26.93,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,That story is something a comedian made up to be funny
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:28.07,Tanaka,Tanaka,0,0,0,,You're still only 50!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.07,0:05:30.31,Endo,Unknown,0,0,0,,You've still got a long way to go
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.31,0:05:33.60,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,Moving on, \N "Pranking Himself Instead of His Junior By Accident"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:35.85,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,Hamada, with his junior from Osaka,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.85,0:05:38.58,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,There's a bookstore he often goes to,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:41.45,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,Leaving his room, Hamada,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.45,0:05:46.33,Tomonori Text,,0,0,0,,He takes his junior's shoes, and throws them really far away,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.33,0:05:49.36,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,This is a signature Hamada prank,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.36,0:05:52.13,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,But recently, and he does this very often,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.13,0:05:55.80,Tomonori Text,Tomonori,0,0,0,,He throws his own shoes away
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.80,0:05:58.37,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.44,0:06:00.14,Hamada,,0,0,0,,HEY! Stop being ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.14,0:06:02.57,Hamada,,0,0,0,,There's no way that's true!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.89,0:06:04.70,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,There's no way that's true
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.70,0:06:05.84,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,I've been told this
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:08.31,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,This is too terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.09,0:06:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Typeset by Shappuri Agemasu Subs \N Translation by senor_wristband
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:23.44,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,"Young Comedians Confess"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:27.43,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,The senility stories continue
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.72,0:06:30.09,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,But really, Hamada,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.14,0:06:32.66,Tomonori Text,Tomonori,0,0,0,,He does care a lot about his juniors' birthdays
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:36.04,Tomonori Text,Tomonori,0,0,0,,He's a kind senpai
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:36.37,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.51,0:06:38.84,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,First off, \N "Forgetting a Birthday #1"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.51,0:06:40.51,Endo,,0,0,0,,There's 1 and 2
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.26,0:06:41.48,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,There is a 1 and 2,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.48,0:06:44.52,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,There a junior named Hirai, who's birthday Hamada went to,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:48.36,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,And 2 days after, Hamada called him up,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.42,0:06:52.39,Tomonori Text,Tomonori,0,0,0,,"When is your birthday again?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:54.43,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,Piss off!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.46,0:07:00.23,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,There's no way that happened
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.82,0:07:03.64,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,Is it possible to be that dumb?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.97,0:07:06.50,Tomonori,,0,0,0,,It was a kind thing to ask, but yes after 2 days
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.80,0:07:06.50,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,After 2 days?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:09.92,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,And if it was Wednesday, he asked on Friday
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.50,0:07:08.80,Matsumoto,Matsumoto,0,0,0,,If it was Monday, he asked on Wednesday
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.01,0:07:13.21,Tomonori,,0,0,0,,"Forgetting a Birthday #2"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.21,0:07:14.49,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,This story,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.49,0:07:18.07,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,One day one of Hamada's juniors suddenly got a call from him,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.07,0:07:20.24,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,Hamada called him up
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.24,0:07:24.48,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,"Did you know it was Taiki's birthday yesterday?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:27.36,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,"If we don't do something for him he's gonna be sad,"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.36,0:07:28.56,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,"Let's have a party for him"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.56,0:07:29.56,Endo,Endo,0,0,0,,Very kind
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.56,0:07:34.95,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,"I'll decide on a place and call you later" \N Very kind senpai indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.95,0:07:39.54,Tomonori Text,Tomonori,0,0,0,,He hasn't called him back for 2 years
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.74,0:07:44.04,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:48.20,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:46.88,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Terrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.09,0:07:51.74,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,Comedians are funny huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:56.96,Matsumoto,Matsumoto,0,0,0,,2 years, so close to 700 days?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.44,0:07:55.45,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,700 days without a call back
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.82,0:07:56.59,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,A surprise?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.79,0:07:56.96,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.01,0:07:59.28,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,Funny, very funny \N As expected of comedians
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.28,0:08:00.98,Tomonori,Unknown,0,0,0,,So moving on,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.98,0:08:03.26,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,"They're Senile As a Couple"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.09,0:08:04.09,Sign,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.26,0:08:10.08,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,From one of his juniors,\N At Nozowa Naoki's birthday,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.08,0:08:17.01,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,When Hamada reached over to remove a rice grain stuck on his wife's face,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.38,0:08:23.18,Tomonori Text,Tomonori,0,0,0,,She thought he was gonna smack her and was very scared
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.05,0:08:28.99,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,You piss off!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:31.46,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,She was like this
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.23,0:08:33.18,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,Knock it off I'm saying
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:37.43,Tomonori Text,Tomonori,0,0,0,,Both of them are senile
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.64,0:08:42.30,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,Incidentally, Hamada is really into using LINE,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.90,0:08:46.92,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,There's a stamp that Yoshimoto put out,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.91,0:08:52.87,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,A stamp of himself farting, and apparently he really loves it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.87,0:08:57.28,Tomonori Text,Tomonori,0,0,0,,Whenever he wants to reply "No" to his wife he sends it to her
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.08,0:09:01.62,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Why, why does he do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.65,0:09:03.25,Tomonori Text,Tomonori,0,0,0,,He farts at home,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.25,0:09:05.72,Tomonori Text,Tomonori,0,0,0,,and farts on LINE,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.72,0:09:08.09,Matsumoto,Matsumoto,0,0,0,,And then his wife gets scared when she sees it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.09,0:09:10.46,Tomonori Text,,0,0,0,,She thinks she's gonna get smacked
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.43,0:09:14.92,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Next, an anti aging story
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.92,0:09:18.57,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Another shocking revelation awaits
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:20.64,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,Hamada, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.64,0:09:27.98,Tomonori Text,Tomonori,0,0,0,,He wants to bring back the cute Hamada of the past
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.64,0:09:26.38,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:27.98,Yamasaki,Yamasaki,0,0,0,,He wants to be cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:32.68,Yamasaki,Yamasaki,0,0,0,,Restoring his cuteness at this age?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:34.79,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,He wants to bring back the cute Hama-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.79,0:09:38.02,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,He's desperately trying different things, like this here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.02,0:09:40.86,Sign,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.36,0:09:40.86,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,"An Unwavering Faith In Garlic"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.86,0:09:42.29,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What the hell is that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:45.90,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,He just straight up loves garlic
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.20,0:09:50.87,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Sounds very stupid
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:51.87,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,He will order a dish with garlic in it wherever he goes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:53.77,Yamasaki,Yamasaki,0,0,0,,An unwavering faith
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.77,0:09:54.94,Tomonori,,0,0,0,,Absolutely
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.26,0:09:58.18,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,That is a bad way to say that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.18,0:10:03.31,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,If you go out for BBQ and they have some garlic side of course you'll order it
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.31,0:10:05.52,Tomonori Text,Tomonori,0,0,0,,An unwavering faith
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.61,0:10:05.45,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,That's all that means
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.52,0:10:08.32,Tomonori Text,Tomonori,0,0,0,,That's why it says "Unwavering faith"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.49,0:10:11.44,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,Stop using stuff like "Unwavering Faith"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.26,0:10:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.99,0:10:14.52,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,Everyone orders garlic
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.52,0:10:16.83,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,I don't really believe in garlic that much
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:20.13,Matsumoto,Matsumoto,0,0,0,,It makes you seem cute so it's OK
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.16,0:10:21.76,Tomonori,Unknown,0,0,0,,This is a nice thing
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.17,0:10:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:23.65,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,So the second thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.65,0:10:25.60,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,"He Uses Face Masks for His Skin"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:28.79,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,This one,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.79,0:10:29.77,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,I get it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.95,0:10:31.48,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,This one is true
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.48,0:10:33.61,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,I admit this one
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.27,0:10:35.82,Endo,Endo,0,0,0,,Have you done this anti-aging stuff recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:39.58,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,If I go golfing, after I come back,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.58,0:10:41.16,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,I will for sure do it then
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.90,0:10:43.88,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,A picture of that moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:48.34,Default,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's Jason
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.07,0:10:54.73,Tomonori Text,Tomonori,0,0,0,,And you're sending a fart here
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:54.60,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.60,0:10:56.50,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,I don't know about that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.84,0:11:00.37,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,Let's move on to the last bit, \N A "Title" for Hamada
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.71,0:11:02.68,Tomonori Text,Tomonori,0,0,0,,In order to cement his position,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:06.40,Tomonori Text,Tomonori,0,0,0,,He's asked his juniors to refer to him by a title
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.85,0:11:08.78,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Oh no
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.40,0:11:08.12,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,"Call me this"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.99,0:11:12.66,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,You're all familiar with these titles,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.66,0:11:14.38,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,Yeah you guys know this
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.38,0:11:18.24,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,Hagimoto Kinichi is called "Colonel",
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:19.83,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,Takeshi-san is "Tono" (Lord)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.30,0:11:21.83,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,Sanma-san is "Waka" (Young Lord)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.61,0:11:23.69,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.69,0:11:25.13,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,Hamada Masatoshi,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.13,0:11:28.54,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,This is what he's told his juniors to call him,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:31.16,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,Here we go, \N "CEO"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.93,0:11:38.21,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,Is he a CEO?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.21,0:11:40.40,Tomonori,Tomonori,0,0,0,,This is not a lie right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.40,0:11:41.52,Matsumoto,Matsumoto,0,0,0,,This is true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.52,0:11:43.28,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,Well, yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.28,0:11:46.55,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,We were talking about "Should we decide a title?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.74,0:11:52.49,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,And before that, on some TV show or something Matsumoto-san called me that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:57.12,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,So using that I said "Call me CEO",
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.12,0:11:58.21,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.46,0:12:02.13,Matsumoto,Matsumoto,0,0,0,,So this is not a lie then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.09,0:12:02.15,Matsumoto,Matsumoto,0,0,0,,This is not a lie right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.87,0:12:06.57,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,What's with that desperate attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.84,0:12:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is he mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.58,0:12:15.81,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,I said "Hahaha Call me CEO!" \N I said THAT!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.81,0:12:17.05,Endo,Hamada,0,0,0,,Well you did tell us
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:22.53,Matsumoto,Matsumoto,0,0,0,,Alright, alright,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.53,0:12:24.32,Matsumoto,Matsumoto,0,0,0,,We'll let that one go
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.89,0:12:27.79,Matsumoto,Matsumoto,0,0,0,,And it makes you look cute so it's alright
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.79,0:12:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Memory Related Incidents
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.20,0:12:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Incident #1
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:40.74,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,An incident when Hamada and his juniors went out for Karaoke
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:45.08,Default,Unknown,0,0,0,,"Mazinger, Mazinger,"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.48,0:12:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,"Mazinger Z!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.21,0:12:52.50,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,"OK! I won't lose to anyone!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.69,0:13:01.23,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,"Tonight, I'm gonna drop you"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.39,0:13:03.90,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,"I sang my heart out"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.90,0:13:06.76,Default,Unknown,0,0,0,,"As expected Hamada-san, you're good!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:07.89,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,"Right?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:10.50,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,"You guys sing your heart out too!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.64,0:13:12.67,Default,Unknown,0,0,0,,"Yes, thank you very much!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.00,0:13:16.74,Default,Unknown,0,0,0,,"Alright, I'll sing Mazinger-Z again and do better!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.91,0:13:17.61,Default,Unknown,0,0,0,,"Okay!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.76,0:13:20.61,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Right before the junior was about to sing,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.45,0:13:27.26,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,"OI! YOU JUST SANG THAT SONG!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.26,0:13:29.69,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,"DON'T SING THE SAME SONG TWICE AT MY KARAOKE PARTY"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.69,0:13:34.16,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,"SCUMBAG! I'LL KICK YOUR ASS!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.76,0:13:35.46,Default,Unknown,0,0,0,,"Sorry! I won't do it again!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.78,0:13:39.96,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Hamada unleashed on the junior
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.55,0:13:42.77,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,{\pos(646.881,902.928)}So scary
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:42.67,Hamada,,0,0,0,,"Whatever, can I sing now?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.42,0:13:45.27,Default,Unknown,0,0,0,,"Yes, please!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.83,0:13:48.69,Hamada,Unknown,0,0,0,,"What should I pick"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:50.47,Endo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1188.56,353.978)}Please, please don't
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.69,0:13:51.11,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,"OK I got it"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:52.31,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1239.295,346.022)}Please stop
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.94,0:13:53.38,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,And then,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.57,0:13:58.07,Default,Unknown,0,0,0,,"Hmm, is this ..."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:06.32,Tomonori Text,Tomonori,0,0,0,,If it's not a joke, then this is unnerving
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.59,0:14:11.34,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Hamada sang Hikigane once again in high spirits
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.43,0:14:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Incident #2
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.45,0:14:17.19,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,This New Years,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.00,0:14:19.00,Hamada,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1106.487,344.033)}What kind of house is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.19,0:14:22.31,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Hamada's juniors went to his house to hang out
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.31,0:14:25.54,Default,Unknown,0,0,0,,"Hamda-san, Happy New Years!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.54,0:14:28.82,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,"Oh, you guys are here! Come in"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:32.08,Default,Unknown,0,0,0,,"Your house is huge!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.08,0:14:34.32,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,It's nothing special!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.25,0:14:38.85,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,And then,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:40.79,Yamasaki,,0,0,0,,Cause he's an idiot
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.09,0:14:43.77,Default,Unknown,0,0,0,,"Happy New Years!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.77,0:14:47.00,Default,Unknown,0,0,0,,"Ah Natsumi-san, Happy New Years!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.00,0:14:49.46,Default,Unknown,0,0,0,,"Make yourselves at home today!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.46,0:14:51.94,Default,Unknown,0,0,0,,"OK! Thank you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.34,0:14:54.21,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,And then,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.32,0:14:58.70,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,The Hamada household's lively puppies
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:03.28,Default,Unknown,0,0,0,,"Hamada-san, you have dogs?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.28,0:15:06.28,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,"Yup, they're so cute right?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.68,0:15:12.87,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Hamada cared for his 3 dogs like they were his own family
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.67,0:15:16.33,Default,Unknown,0,0,0,,"I really love dogs!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.36,0:15:18.40,Default,Unknown,0,0,0,,"What are their names?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:20.76,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,"You asked a great question!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.76,0:15:23.34,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,"I'm only gonna say this once, so pay attention,"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.34,0:15:26.23,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,This big one is Kiyonu,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.23,0:15:28.04,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,This one is Ribbon,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.04,0:15:30.65,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,and this little guy here is De Niro
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.65,0:15:33.08,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,"They're so cute right?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.28,0:15:38.48,Default,Unknown,0,0,0,,"That's not it at all!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.48,0:15:41.68,Default,Unknown,0,0,0,,"The biggest one is De Niro!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.68,0:15:44.57,Default,Unknown,0,0,0,,"And this boy is Kiyonu!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.08,0:15:47.85,Default,Unknown,0,0,0,,"And the small one is Ribbon, right?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.19,0:15:52.18,Default,Unknown,0,0,0,,"Just when will you remember?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.43,0:15:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.27,0:16:02.44,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,It seems Hamada doesn't know his beloved dogs' names
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Incident #3
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.85,0:16:09.05,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.95,0:16:16.05,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,This incident happened when Hamada and his juniors went to play golf
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.40,0:16:19.29,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,Golf is awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.58,0:16:22.24,Default,Unknown,0,0,0,,"Hamada-san, you're in high spirits today!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.24,0:16:23.51,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,"That's right,"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.56,0:16:25.40,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,"The ball went really far too"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.49,0:16:30.87,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Hamada on that day was feeling his best
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.87,0:16:34.31,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,They went through the course in high spirits,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.31,0:16:35.44,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,And then,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.88,0:16:39.14,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,"Okay, starting from now, English is banned"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:44.52,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,"You have to pay a 100 yen penalty for every English word"\N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.52,0:16:47.37,Default,Hamada,0,0,0,,"Ehh, that's so hard"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.37,0:16:48.93,Default,Unknown,0,0,0,,"By the way, Hamada-san,"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.93,0:16:51.56,Default,Unknown,0,0,0,,"What should we call the driver?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.56,0:16:57.39,Hamada,Hamada,0,0,0,,That's easy! That's the pushy thing, or the "Eldest Son"
